{"type": "article", "id": 15324, "title": "防身钥匙扣", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-23T06:50:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140505Q9pwIhtlNS3EnzRv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t防身用品也是旅行中必不可少的，尤其是女生。挪威Safe+推出过一系列的防身配件，这里是其中一个具有报警功能的钥匙扣。只要按下底部的按钮，就能激活报警器，发出高分贝的报警声。必要时，拉紧钥匙环使绳子抽紧，钥匙就会立起来变成一个简易的防身武器。有黑白两种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81Safe-%E9%92%A5%E5%8C%99%E6%89%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%8A%A5%E5%99%A8-%E9%98%B2%E8%BA%AB%E6%89%93%E5%87%BB%E5%99%A8/dp/B012V8CKG0/ref=pd_sim_sbs_200_1?ie=UTF8&amp;refRID=1SAM7ME39TPPWJXHYC1X\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142534a6x2AmoFtHU8r3ep.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142535jlmyNOpkDI2Uio83.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142535Yv3UlikKzMD8cm4q.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}